data.description: This single family home is located in the cozy neighborhood of Garden Acres in Pooler with NO HOA! This home sits on a cul de sac tucked in the back of the neighborhood which means little to no vehicle traffic. The neighborhood is located in central Pooler off of S Rogers st, across from the Pooler Fire Headquarters station. Fast access to I95 and I16. There is laminate floor throughout the house except the master bedroom which is carpet. A brand new roof was also installed on April 1st. There is also a nice side/back porch to enjoy a cup of joe in the mornings, or watch your kids play in the yard. Dont miss out on this deal, everything is cooler in Pooler!
